{"word":"H5895 - עַיִר - ʻayir - ah'-yeer - Colt","slug":"H5895","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עַיִר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻayir"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ah'-yeer"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Colt"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E2;&#x05D9;&#x05E8; - &#x201B;ayir</b> - <i>ah'-yeer</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H5782\">H5782</a> in the sense of <i>raising</i> (that is, <i>bearing</i> a burden); properly a young <i>ass</i> (as just broken to a load); hence an ass <i>colt: - </i>(ass) colt, foal, young ass."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5896\">H5896</a>, <a href=\"#/H5897\">H5897</a>, <a href=\"#/H5900\">H5900</a>, <a href=\"#/H5901\">H5901</a>, <a href=\"#/H5902\">H5902</a>, <a href=\"#/H5906\">H5906</a>, <a href=\"#/H5907\">H5907</a>, <a href=\"#/H5908\">H5908</a>, <a href=\"#/H5909\">H5909</a>, <a href=\"#/H5910\">H5910</a>"}]}